</pre></td><td class="code"><pre>  <span class="nt">&lt;div&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>
      An anthologie of fine stories inspir‚Äôd
      by the <span class="nt">&lt;strong&gt;</span>Bard of Stratford<span class="nt">&lt;/strong&gt;</span> and the Lovecraftian Mythos
